10400:Black, blackiest-black delusions...? What do you mean...?\p;
10500:Regardless of what she meant, staying here wasn't an option.\n;With Rimi's corpse lying here, anyone who spotted us would find out exactly what we'd done.\p;
10600:So, without getting an answer from her, I lent Kozupii my shoulder, and the two of us began to leave the school.\p;
